New Construction vs Resale: The Strategic Difference

Here’s what no one explains clearly.

New Construction

Pros:
	•	Builder incentives
	•	Warranty coverage
	•	Rate buydowns
	•	Minimal repairs early on

Cons:
	•	You must understand contract terms
	•	Builder reps represent the builder

Having representation matters more in new construction — not less.

⸻

Resale Homes

Pros:
	•	Established landscaping
	•	Larger lots in many cases
	•	Potential negotiation room
	•	No HOA options in some areas

Cons:
	•	Roof age
	•	Insurance considerations
	•	Inspection discoveries

The smartest move isn’t choosing randomly.

It’s aligning your purchase with your long-term goals.

